WEBVTT

00:04:28.320 --> 00:04:30.240
that til death do us part,

00:04:31.240 --> 00:04:32.480
I will be there.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:36.400
If needed, I will speak for you.

00:04:37.200 --> 00:04:39.480
I will honor your wishes.

00:04:41.280 --> 00:04:44.640
That paperwork became
a tangible part of our love story.

00:04:47.040 --> 00:04:48.256
As physicians,

00:04:48.280 --> 00:04:49.936
Paul and I were in a good position

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:53.120
to understand and even
accept his diagnosis.

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:55.456
We weren't angry about it,

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:56.696
luckily,

00:04:56.720 --> 00:05:00.856
because we'd seen so many patients
in devastating situations,